		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/7999.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 21 Jul 2023 07:13:04 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[寒性]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[寒热]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[水果]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.huacao77.com/?p=7999</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[有时候你会发现有莫名其妙的牙痛、眼睛红肿、口角发炎等，其实这就可能是吃多了某种水果； 而有些人的体质，如果吃多 [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">有时候你会发现有莫名其妙的牙痛、眼睛红肿、口角发炎等，其实这就可能是吃多了某种水果；</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">而有些人的体质，如果吃多了某些水果，就容易胃不舒服、拉肚子，导致消化功能紊乱。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">为什么呢？</strong></p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/17ef5e003bc0f2f625203f3d5e00baa5.gif" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">其实水果再好，吃不对也伤身！这是因为水果也分寒热性。</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">比如我们常说的“桃养人，杏伤人，李子树下埋死人”，这里面的道理就是与水果的寒热性有关：</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">“李子、杏”这两种属于寒性的水果，吃的过多容易导致胃寒。如果是胃寒、体寒的人吃多了这些寒性水果，身体往往难以承受，出现腹泻等问题。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">水果分寒热，名单要记牢</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">水果主要分为三类：<strong style="color: blue;">寒性、温性、热性</strong>。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">寒性水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">——解燥热</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">典型代表：</strong>西瓜、山竹、香瓜、梨、香蕉、猕猴桃、柿子、香蕉、奇异果、甜瓜、椰子、圣女果等。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">寒性水果属于偏寒性的，有助于解燥热、清热火，对于面红目赤、牙龈肿痛、口干渴、小便短赤、大便燥结、舌红苔黄燥等实火病症，有很好的缓解效果。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/83c98c6e8ece7a88a68644add5022a15.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1fe7ca3b678e8ebe5c0d407bb231814d.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温性水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">——最养人</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">典型代表：</strong>苹果、葡萄、甘蔗、百香果、柠檬、番石榴、凤梨、木瓜、橄榄、菠萝、芒果等。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/b3818f4e99df941f594fccfb2582fa04.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">温性水果比较和平，适用大多数人食用。一般属温性的水果可以多吃一些。这类水果有温热补益的作用，祛寒补虚、消除寒症，增加人体热量，促进人体能量代谢。</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">热性水果</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">——驱寒健体</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">典型代表：</strong>荔枝、桃子、龙眼、樱桃、大枣、榴莲、木瓜、橘子、芦柑等。</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/60f11e7886760957f67e2fec5df102b2.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/916508f080c405b13f23d80f1d5bb185.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">不同水果，挑法不同</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">西 瓜 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">底部圈圈越大皮就越厚，蒂头卷曲的更甜！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e33a1bd391d0357350ebb5b3df1dfc7b.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/02bc49a9285a8db2ea37e9a260736f18.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">山 竹 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">屁股上几个瓣果肉就有几个瓣，瓣多的籽小；果蒂绿的新鲜！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/f7c4a3cedf9962b3a7d5fae03b51f957.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/9ce41d13435cd5476e96fe1607aa4de4.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">桃 子 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">果体大饱满的味好汁，闻起来有清香的更甜，手感微软的熟到刚好~</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/22e8ec50c21e6ad6d67726716ac16c0d.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/bf029f2e0b1b54e76ff0afc6ce6ebda4.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">荔 枝 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">外壳龟裂片平坦、缝合线明显的成熟度高；闻起来有酒味，或是酸味说明已经不新鲜了～</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/409e197635422f55a85732e0ab1f516e.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/672acdf108c1de858a404d4ed166de3a.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">火龙果 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">不要瘦子，越胖代表越成熟，肉质越多，越甜~</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/af6fa7a0b83f6a52212495b08a826978.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">橙 子 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">同等大小重的好，硬的比软的好！毛孔粗大的是大厚皮，肚脐小的口感好！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1ca08b14c01959abcaede712ad3c63f0.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">木 瓜 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">肚子大的比较甜！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/51a3083e922640bb2e0c8a0520f244f8.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">榴 莲 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">壳薄的肉多，同样大小，轻的核小；皮上的小山丘越多肉越多！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/e1424ca88d0410aa0d699e576c4ecd58.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">香 蕉 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">两头绿的是处理过的，不要有棱角的！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/83e44b19d11f0c86211b36c512271f1b.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">芒 果 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">有斑点的是从里边烂掉了，果蒂不能出水，果皮不能起皱～</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7420a04fed31ffcd96aec78620e067ab.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;"><strong style="color: blue;">哈密瓜 </strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 40px; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 30px;">网纹较粗而且密集的是好瓜，屁股凹进去的是好瓜！</p>
    <div style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;"><img decoding="async" src="/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/7b8e59e6a9bff7747e61e628ad184d52.png" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>


</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
